Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Opon District Hospital in the City of Lapu-Lapu to Lapu-Lapu City District Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 838
An Act Changing the Name of the Opon District Hospital in the City of Lapu-Lapu to Lapu-Lapu City District Hospital
Section 1. The name of the Opon District Hospital in the City of Lapu-Lapu is hereby changed to Lapu-Lapu City District Hospital.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
